        {
            "title": "亞洲股市追隨華爾街創新高上漲;伊朗局勢擔憂限制漲幅",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/bMo16XK1NpffKOKUMxtxLg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPEB0I07L_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com- 亞洲股市週五在假期清淡交易中上漲,追隨華爾街創紀錄收盤,同時投資者謹慎關注美國與伊朗持續衝突的最新發展。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">由於中國、香港、新加坡和印度等主要市場因公眾假期休市,交易量較為清淡。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">區域股市受到美股強勁表現的提振,標普500指數和納斯達克綜合指數創下新高,受到樂觀企業財報和油價回落的支撐。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">收盤後,蘋果公司公佈的季度業績超出預期,提振了科技股的市場情緒。</p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\"><strong>伊朗警告將報復,傳局勢可能進一步升級</strong></h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">日本日經225指數週五上漲0.6%,而較廣泛的東證指數則持平。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-99a5c268-4f38-3300-876e-9113415fd0b4-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">漲幅受到地緣政治風險升高的限制。報導指出,美國總統唐納德·川普將聽取有關針對伊朗潛在軍事行動的簡報,引發對局勢進一步升級的擔憂。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">伊朗警告稱,任何新的美國攻擊都將引發對該地區美國陣地的「長期而痛苦的打擊」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">荷莫茲海峽實際上仍處於關閉狀態,擾亂了全球石油運輸的重要航線,並加劇了供應緊張預期。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">布蘭特原油週四早些時候曾飆升至每桶超過126美元——創下四年來最高水平——但隨後在當天稍晚回落。</p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\"><strong>亞洲市場4月表現強勁</strong></h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">亞洲市場在4月錄得強勁的月度漲幅,當時股市在人工智慧相關增長樂觀情緒以及美伊臨時停火後恐慌情緒緩解的推動下大幅上漲。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">韓國KOSPI指數上月飆升超過30%,而日本日經指數則飆升超過15%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">中國上證綜合指數在4月攀升近6%,印度Nifty 50指數上漲7.5%。</p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\"><strong>東京4月CPI仍低於日本央行目標</strong></h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">東京消費者通膨在4月溫和上升,而潛在價格壓力有所放緩,仍低於日本央行的目標,凸顯需求狀況疲弱。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">數據顯示,首都4月整體消費者價格年增1.5%,較3月的1.4%略有上升。剔除新鮮食品的核心CPI上升1.5%,較1.7%放緩,並低於市場預期的1.8%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">日本央行最近維持利率不變,但釋出鷹派傾向信號,市場預期最早可能在6月升息。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">澳洲S&amp;P/ASX 200指數上漲0.9%,Coles Group (ASX:COL)公佈第三季銷售額增長3.1%,受強勁的超市增長和電子商務需求推動,儘管其酒類業務仍然疲軟。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BA%9E%E6%B4%B2%E8%82%A1%E5%B8%82%E8%BF%BD%E9%9A%A8%E8%8F%AF%E7%88%BE%E8%A1%97%E5%89%B5%E6%96%B0%E9%AB%98%E4%B8%8A%E6%BC%B2-%E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%97%E5%B1%80%E5%8B%A2%E6%93%94%E6%86%82%E9%99%90%E5%88%B6%E6%BC%B2%E5%B9%85-041213760.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-05-01 12:20:38",
